Usage: read_codesign_die_abstract [-help] <DIEABSTRACTFILE> [-check_only]
                                  [-no_diff]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<DIEABSTRACTFILE>     # name of the die abstract file (string, required)
-check_only           # This is only valid with the -no_diff option. If these
                      # two options are given, then the difference viewer will
                      # not be used, and the EDI db will not be updated
                      # (bool, optional)
-no_diff              # when given, the difference viewer will not be utilized.
                      # The die abstract will be read and the db updated with
                      # all the changes unless the -check_only option is
                      # provided. (bool, optional)